<br>
Second you almost always get parchments through raids, which makes going on almost ANY raid in pop benefical to casters as well as melee.   No more silly vindi raids that are all melee, and no more velk raids that are all caster.  You need both to do raids anyway, and it's a smart way of getting both.<br>
<br>
....<br>
<br>
Ok that said..<br>
<br>
Theres a few spells that caster classes do NEED.   For mages its our pets.  For wizards it's their nukes, and clerics need the heal spells to keep players going etc.   There should be soloable and questable spells that encompass this for each class.   Players should not have to wait for these parchments for such key spells.<br>
<br>
In that sense and that only the parchment thing is off.<br>
<br>
But I'm alone I guess on that opinion. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=soulcraver>Soulcraver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#333333>(10/31/02 12:35:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=143.topic&index=63>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsdown.gif" align=absmiddle>  A game</span><hr size=1> Sirellyn,<br>
<br>
First this is not real life, it is a game.  If the majority of people say it is bad then it should be changed.  you can't do that in life but you can do that in a game.  Just think if the majority of a software company's client base said, &quot;in order for us to continue to use this you need to add &quot;X&quot; functionality to it.&quot;  Then the software company said, &quot;hey we think it's just right so we're not changing a thing&quot;<br>
<br>
Unfortunately, VI doesn't have any real competition so they are not threatened by their player base but that example demonstrates my point.<br>
<br>
Second, I'm in a guild whose player base is mainly European and they are just getting the game as are other international players.  The situation is only gonna get worse with more players coming in that need the same parchments.  That also has made it impossible for us to raid PoP targets because of lack of people PoP capable.  That will change soon but so will competition increase.<br>
<br>
Bottom line is the level 61-62 spells should be dirt common.  All non-VT capable players, which is 90%+ of the player base, need those spells to compete well.  The level 63-64 should be tougher to get and that will separate the mid/high level players from the more casual player.  Level 65 spells should be dropping more off boss mobs and that will further separate the pack.<br>
<br>
Finally, it just isn't fun being a caster class when you don't have ANY of your spells.  Why would a company create a situation that causes this kind of tension.  Now that they know it they can make appropriate changes.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showMessageRange?topicID=143.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showMessageRange?topicID=143.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showMessageRange?topicID=143.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showPrevMessage?topicID=143.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showNextMessage?topicID=143.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=143.topic&index=63><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.threadControl?topicID=143.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=143.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=143.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=p